  "description": "<p>为了让移动设备可以更加地轻薄，厂商们已经绞尽脑汁。<strong>周三的时候，LG Display宣布，它们已经做出了号称\"世界</strong><strong>上最薄的智能手机全高清液晶面板\"。该面板的长度为5.2英寸(约13.2cm)，厚度仅2.2毫米。</strong>LG表示，通过触摸技术、双柔性印刷电路和直接贴合系统，面板在提升更高亮度的同时，更减少了30%的排线。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e7fca8b/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244306.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DLG%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E8%96%84%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244306.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DLG%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E8%96%84%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244306.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DLG%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E8%96%84%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244306.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DLG%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E8%96%84%E7%9A%84%E5%85%A8%E9%AB%98%E6%B8%85%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%B6%B2%E6%99%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%9D%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feeds